{"tid":1924006,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被毆男求頒令披露警身份","createTime":"2020-03-13T11:53:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T13:27:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fa825ac60b1fd4caf6ce789ac8848c703e87cfeb","tid":1924006,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:53:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200313/XJPLQBRIVRCXQ6U4YNXJFQ7GCU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200313%2FXJPLQBRIVRCXQ6U4YNXJFQ7GCU%2F&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j56X7PLg0GRX82CuX%2BG2FI0%3D&h=2717a00e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200313%2FXJPLQBRIVRCXQ6U4YNXJFQ7GCU%2F&h=affebdc5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200313/XJPLQBRIVRCXQ6U4YNXJFQ7GCU/</a><br />\n<br />\n被毆男求頒令披露警身份<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200313/large/1584044289_4c54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200313%2Flarge%2F1584044289_4c54.jpg&h=5510f1ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n申請人吳康聯日前入稟高等法院，要求下令警方以誓章形式披露扯跌他並對他拳打腳踢的警員身份。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】反送中運動至今九個月，警方屢遭批評濫權濫暴，大部份防暴警與速龍小隊執勤時，更拒絕展示警員編號，即使傳媒拍下警暴過程，事主也無從追討。有市民去年6.12在金鐘夏愨道突遭一批蒙面速龍扯跌、並被亂棍毆打兼狂踢，該市民日前入稟高等法院，要求法庭下令警方以誓章形式披露涉事警員身份，並交出警方行動紀錄、警員記事冊等與事件有關文件，以便提出索償及向執法部門和有關機構投訴。<br />\n<br />\n以便提出法律訴訟<br />\n<br />\n申請人吳康聯（51歲）透過律師入稟，答辯人是警務處處長鄧炳強。吳早於去年9月已聯袂另外兩名事主申請司法覆核，要求法庭裁定速龍小隊和防暴警有系統並持續地拒絕展示編號，違反《人權法》，該案已定於本月27日進行司法覆核許可聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n至於本案，吳要求法庭下令警方以誓章形式，披露所有6月12日當天下午3時許，在夏愨道與添華道交界橋底扯跌他並對他拳打腳踢的警員身份，包括姓名、警員編號和地址。<br />\n<br />\n此外，吳要求警方交出所有與事件有關的文件，包括警方行動紀錄、備忘錄、會議紀錄、報告、流水簿、警員記事冊等，及任何電子檔案文件，並容許其代表律師查閱和影印有關文件。吳同時要求法庭批准他使用上述資料，以向涉事任何失責警員提出法律訴訟。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCMP243/20<br />\n■記者楊思雅"},{"pid":"96e8daa67edced3821258c1fa4fea0a4bb9eb852","tid":1924006,"uid":114875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:57:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0611f88c3bd7b84c2646a414c8da1b1477c884d9","tid":1924006,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:59:45.000Z","msg":"勇敢"},{"pid":"0ba96650f5410533964c6af13da92015f13d1a69","tid":1924006,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:01:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a350d2365a2808836af2fe1fda3810d8eb6f89","tid":1924006,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:03:50.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98941c413903699bea203e9b7f09dcdc69f5fb02","tid":1924006,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:04:52.000Z","msg":"制度內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3855bf6db0f6cd81cbd862fbcecd3ea87bdaaa62","tid":1924006,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:05:25.000Z","msg":"支持手足"},{"pid":"e1a0efb6935539ae5de23d654663e4d829fb82a2","tid":1924006,"uid":51621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:05:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a443bf99cad5ecdb1962ff8bd76f7e05c1b1683","tid":1924006,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:06:08.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5242e57d5ac56b15fc002ca6dad27c45bccb973b","tid":1924006,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:09:14.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"6cad80dfc9e8348581c0e511b58f51e3217441e1","tid":1924006,"uid":200135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:10:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7d6